async def get_processed(items):
    out = []
    async for x in items:
        out.append(await process(x))
    return out

async def active_users(users):
    active = []
    async for u in users:
        if await u.is_active():
            active.append(u)
    return active

async def upper_stream(items):
    async for x in items:
        yield (await fetch(x)).upper()
